#include <iostream>
#include <stdio.h>

using namespace std;

int main() {
    long long t, n, c, a, b, j;

    cin >> t;

    for (long long i = 0; i < t; i++) {
        cin >> n;
        a = 1;
        b = 1;
        j = 0;
        while(1) {
            if (b == n) {
                j = 1;
                break;
            }

            c = a + b;
            a = b;
            b = c;

            if (b > n) {
                break;
            }
        }
        if (j == 1) {
            cout << "is fibo\n";
        } else {
            cout << "not fibo\n";
        }
    }
    return 0;
}
